dct_title_s: Insurance maps of South Orange Village, including South Orange and Millburn Townships, New Jersey (Sheet 55)
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key map, streets and specials index, and text. "5119." South Orange Village and Township are identical and coextensive with South Orange, a census desig. place; P.O. name South Orange. cf. Rand McNally comm. atlas, 1991. Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-7, 31-32, 41-44, and 46-66 of South Orange Village series, showing South Orange Township.
